Description: Foundry Linux base layer — full kit, devbox image preinstall
 The base "Foundry Linux" install for game-makers, level designers,
 and digital artists: the WorldFoundry authoring stack (Blender + 10
 WF CLIs + WF Blender add-ons), the retro-porting toolkit (MAME,
 Ghidra, dasm, z80, cc65, ...), light universe emulators, game-dev
 frameworks (SDL2/3, SFML, Allegro, libtcod, Tiled, LOVE + Vulkan
 shader tools), CLI image utilities, and go-task. Single command,
 the whole working environment.
 .
 The Foundry Linux devbox container image (ghcr.io/foundry-linux/devbox:26.04)
 installs this and nothing else; sprite and atelier are layered on top
 inside a running container if wanted.
 .
 Cross-Depends on apt.worldfoundry.org (worldfoundry); the bootstrap
 setup.sh wires up both apt sources and the Cloudsmith task repo.
